WORK FLOW OF POWER BI

Raw data
 (connect data
     +
 Clean data )
     ↓
Modelling
(Relationships)
     ↓
Calculations
     ↓
Visualization
     ↓
  Reports
     ↓
  Publish
     ↓
 Dashboards
(app.powerbi.com)

Workflow of power bi :
● Connect data from different sources .
● After connecting data from different sources in different formats we have to clean that data.
● After cleaning the data we have to model our data in order to establish relationships.
● After providing relationships we have to perform calculations(By using DAX).
● After that we are going to visualize our data in the form of pictorial representation like charts , graphs , maps .
● After visualization we have publish.
